humanMachineDialogue.text: The patient has one sentinel lymph node (AJCC pN1mi) that is positive for tumor, and multiple other left axillary lymph nodes (AJCC pNO) that are negative for tumor. This indicates a pathologic N stage of N1, based on the AJCC staging system.
